_sText: One of those concrete barricades that are in a lot of games (this one was modeled after the Battlefield 3 ones). It's 68x68, but you know, you can make it fit your 64x64 grid no problem if you are worried about that. Made this for my map dm seine crossing which was modeled after the Seine Crossing map in Battlefield 3. It is pretty heavy on brush faces so I wouldn't spam them all over your map if you're making a larger one that may be hitting the brush limit. If you use this please make sure to credit me for it. Thank you.
